Package com.onlineStoreCom.entity.order

Class Order

java.lang.Object
com.onlineStoreCom.entity.setting.subsetting.IdBasedEntity
com.onlineStoreCom.entity.address.AbstractAddress
com.onlineStoreCom.entity.order.Order
@Entity public class Order extends AbstractAddress
Represents a customer order in the e-commerce system.

This class extends AbstractAddress to include shipping information and contains order details such as items, costs, payment method, and status. Orders are associated with customers and can have multiple order details and tracks.
